        {
            "title": "美伊又要打起來了？川普不排除空襲伊朗、伊軍方稱已為開戰做好準備",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/E9iwo6.g4spWsw6zQt9Ang--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/cnyes_hk_559/d4d59484fb843d974b6e63fc5389719b\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E4%BC%8A%E5%8F%88%E8%A6%81%E6%89%93%E8%B5%B7%E4%BE%86%E4%BA%86-%E5%B7%9D%E6%99%AE%E4%B8%8D%E6%8E%92%E9%99%A4%E7%A9%BA%E8%A5%B2%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97-%E4%BC%8A%E8%BB%8D%E6%96%B9%E7%A8%B1%E5%B7%B2%E7%82%BA%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B0%E5%81%9A%E5%A5%BD%E6%BA%96%E5%82%99-050003486.html",
